CustomField.inlineHelpText: If populated, all addresses, for the activated objects (Apex Trigger), will be geocoded using this service. Accepted values: "Google" for the Google Geocoding API or "Salesforce Maps" for the Salesforce Maps Geocoder API. If empty, Data Integration Rules will be used or country specific configurations as defined in the custom metadata: "Geocoding Country Config"
CustomField.label: Geocoding Service
